    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 550ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[700ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [950ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong></p>",
