    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leek has softened, add your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Add the<strong> vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> and cook for 15-18 min or until the potatoes are almost fork-tender</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
